          "evidence_text_excerpt": "inal document to:\nB2B Bank\n199 Bay Street, Suite 600\nPO Box 279 STN Commerce Court\nToronto ON M5L 0A2\nFor renewals, fax documents\nto 1.888.946.3448 or mail to\nB2B Bank.\nThe issue date on the investment will\nbe the date the funds are received.\nRate guarantee does not apply\nto post-dated cheques.\nSet up\nauto-renewals\nPrincipal or Principal & Interest can be\nautomatically renewed.\nComplete a Non-Registered GIC\nApplication.\nCheck the auto-renewal box in\nsection 5, under Renewal/Principal\nMaturity Payment instructions.\nFax to 1.888.946.3448. Send renewal instructions at least 30 days\nprior to the maturity date.\nChange how\ninterest payments\nare received\nInterest payments issued by cheque can be\nchanged to electronic funds transfer (EFT) for\nyour client\u2019s convenience.\nComplete the Non-Financial Account\nChanges form and send it along\nwith a void cheque from a personal\nchequing account,",
